"Dictate" = "听写";
"Use Hold to Speak or Tap to Speak. Without a text selection, Typeforme inserts the new result at the cursor." = "使用按住说话或点击说话。没有选中文本时,Typeforme 会在光标处插入新结果。";
"Fix selected text" = "修正选中文本";
"Select the wrong span first, then press the mic and say the intended replacement. Only that selected span is replaced." = "先选中错误片段,再按麦克风说出想替换的内容。只会替换选中的片段。";
"Command edit" = "指令编辑";
"Press the wand and speak an instruction like make this shorter, translate this, or turn it into bullets. With no selection, it targets the current input text." = "点击魔棒后说出指令,例如缩短、翻译或改成项目符号。没有选区时会处理当前输入文本。";
"Restyle existing text" = "改写现有文本";
"Clean, Polish, Polish+, Structure+, and Formal+ use the selected text first, then the current visible input text." = "清洁、润色、润色+、结构+、正式+ 会优先使用选中文本,否则使用当前可见输入文本。";
"Selection changed" = "选区已变化";
"If iOS no longer reports the same selection when the result returns, Typeforme copies the result instead of guessing where to paste it." = "如果结果返回时 iOS 不再报告同一选区,Typeforme 会复制结果,不会猜测粘贴位置。";

